### Updated

- Corrects `RCLink` and `ExternalLink` accessibility attributes [SCC-4149](https://newyorkpubliclibrary.atlassian.net/browse/SCC-4149)
- Updates filters to new sidebar design with live filtering [SCC-4721](https://newyorkpubliclibrary.atlassian.net/browse/SCC-4721)
- Removes redirect for 404s on bib/hold pages and nonexistent paths, instead just displaying 404 view and unchanged URL [SCC-4751](https://newyorkpubliclibrary.atlassian.net/browse/SCC-4751)
- Updates GH actions to require tests before deploying, and consolidates `qa`, `train`, and `prod` deployment scripts [SCC-4272](https://newyorkpubliclibrary.atlassian.net/browse/SCC-4272)

